reviewText: I totally agree with the other two comments. This DVD was a total rip-off. First of all the production was unacceptable for a DVD that was made  recently. Secondly, there were no crowds like normal live DVDs have and also the camera angles weren't very good. Save your money for something else
This was not worth my time in listen to this DVD. It not interesting at all. Transaction was quick an efficient.
I didn't like this DVD at all. It was a very cheaply made DVD!! They still can sing!! But it just wasn't  organized !! To me it was a mess!
